MESSAGE.value: Corrected fixity range for custom operators
Corrected type evaluation of certain expressions
Allowed for adding comments inside function definition groups
Allowed for hiding brackets when using operator as a function
Allowed for specifying negative integer and double values
Updated visuals of the editor
Contructor pattern uses automatic brackets only if it is not inside PBracket from now
Corrected adding/specifying negative literals
Added intention for adding new cases inside the case concept
Added scoping for case concept
Corrected type evaluation of tuples inside annotations
Corrected scope for case concept and added scope to list comprehension
Added additional frege usage examples
Corrected a frege usage example
Corrected type evaluation of an empty list
Corrected textgen for function definition (grouped)
Corrected displaying of referenced operators

Major typesystem revision
- corrected referenced operator type evaluation, which halted with 'when concrete' block never being concrete - corrected most of the exceptions tied to typesystem where a node was not inside the model (FDGrouped - getDefinitionNode, 'when concrete' skips errors for EPBianryExpressions) - most of the redundant 'when concrete' blocks were removed - corrected type evaluation for empty list pattern [] - corrected type enforcement for children patterns in case concept
Corrected NegativeExpression concept type evaluation
Corrected type evaluation of referenced functions
Corrected grammar of importing statements
String type made native
Undecidable type renamed to Unknown
Default precedence of custom infix operators changed to 16
List enumeration to range can be changed only if the .. is written right of the last item of the list
